              Support, services, and other commercial needs for Warewulf are
              available by the project lead and founder along with the primary
              core developers through CIQ (Ctrl IQ, Inc.). CIQ is the leading
              innovator of modernization of high-performance infrastructures and
              cloud-native computing and directly offers support and services of
              several open-source projects like Warewulf, Warewulf, and Rocky
              Linux.
            </dt>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </li>
